Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time spent on cases leading to 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The sum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average resolution time for cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Time difference between 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' for cases where both occur
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' to 'Request Payment' in cases where the declaration is eventually approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Minimum time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Maximum time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and any subsequent 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time for all activities between 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by PRE_APPROVER'

Name: Time from 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' in cases where re-submission leads to approval
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average waiting time before 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' after 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total resolution time of cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' compared to those without
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case
